Others: The Suns lost to the Lakers in their final preseason game, 128-122, in overtime.
Kevin Durant, Devin Booker, and Cameron Payne played 30+ minutes each.
Jusuf Nurkic made his preseason debut, scoring 15 points and grabbing 7 rebounds.
Ryan Dunn played 20 minutes, going 1-of-4 from the field and fouling out.
Bradley Beal struggled offensively, shooting 4-of-15 from the field and 1-of-6 from three.
The regular season begins next Wednesday against the Clippers.
